data.description: Indulge in this amazing and stylish single level townhome centrally located on the Boise Bench, close to downtown, the freeway, the airport and BSU; with no HOA! This is the perfect starter home for those seeking a low maintenance lifestyle or an investment opportunity.  With tons of charm and character, this home is situated on a corner lot, in a peaceful neighborhood , with a one car garage, maintenance free back yard, 2 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms as well as an office that could be used as a 3rd bedroom. Don't miss this opportunity to own a home where comfort and practicality come together in a great location on the desirable Boise Bench!
